<div class="container-fluid banner-container">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-xs-6 ">
     <header class="intro-header">

      <h1 class="text">La solution professionnelle
        <br>pour gérer
        <br>vos planning
        <br>en toute simplicité</h1>
        <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-7 margin">
          <%= simple_form_for(resource, as: resource_name, url: session_path(resource_name)) do |f| %>
          <%= f.input :email, label: false, required: false, placeholder: "Email" %>
          <%= f.input :password, label: false, required: false, placeholder: "Mot de passe" %>
          <%= f.input :remember_me, label: "Se souvenir de moi", as: :boolean if devise_mapping.rememberable? %>
          <%= f.button :submit, "Connexion", class: "form-actions btn-primary btn-home btn-block " %>
          <% end %>

          <%= render "devise/shared/links" %>
        </div>


      </header>
    </div>
    <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
     <%= image_tag("CPPM.jpg", :alt => "planning_ex", class: "image_landing") %>
   </div>
 </div>
</div>

<section class="content-section-0">

  <div class="container">

    <div class="row center">
      <div class="col-xs-offset-4 col-xs-4 lead">
        <%= image_tag "logo.png", alt: "Mon image", width: 150, height: 150 %>
      </div>
      <div class="col-xs-offset-2 col-xs-8">
        <div class="clearfix"></div>
        <p class="lead"><b>Ca <span class="color-word">plan</span> pour moi est un moyen simple pour créer et organiser vos planning.</b>
          <br>Laissez tomber les tableau excel ou papier.
          <br>Ca plan pour moi vous permet de créer un planning qui convient à toute votre équipe en un clin d’oeil.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="container background-container">
    <div class="row">



    <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-3">
        <section class="content-section-a">
         <%= image_tag "wrench.png", alt: "Mon image", width: 150, height: 150 %>

         <div class="clearfix"></div>
         <h2 class="section-heading"><span class="color-word">1</span></h2>
         <p class="lead-etape"><b>Créez la structure de votre planning</b></p>
       </section>
     </div>

     <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-3">
      <section class="content-section-a">
       <%= image_tag "worker.png", alt: "Mon image", width: 150, height: 150 %>

       <div class="clearfix"></div>
       <h2 class="section-heading"><span class="color-word">2</span></h2>
       <p class="lead-etape"><b>Assignez les collaborateurs dont vous avez besoins.</b></p>
     </section>
   </div>

   <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-3">
    <section class="content-section-a">
     <%= image_tag "clipboard.png", alt: "Mon image", width: 150, height: 150 %>

     <div class="clearfix"></div>
     <h2 class="section-heading"><span class="color-word">3</span></h2>
     <p class="lead-etape"><b>Vos collaborateurs rentrent leurs disponibiltés.</b></p>
   </section>
 </div>

 <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-3">
  <section class="content-section-a">
   <%= image_tag "checked.png", alt: "Mon image", width: 150, height: 150 %>

   <div class="clearfix"></div>
   <h2 class="section-heading"><span class="color-word">4</span></h2>
   <p class="lead-etape"><b>Ca plan pour moi s’occupe de créer votre planning.</b></p>
 </section>
</div>

</div>
</div>
